    <div class="news-story">
        






    <h4 class="news-story-title">
        
            <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://hir.harvard.edu/growth-from-genocide-the-story-of-rwandas-healthcare-system/">Growth from Genocide: The Story of Rwanda’s Healthcare System</a>
        
    </h4>

<div class="row">
    
        <div class="news-story-body col-xs-12">
            <div class="news-story-byline">
                
                    
                        <a rel="nofollow" class="timeago" title="Mar 07, 2022" href="/link/oOZpof/growth-from-genocide-the-story-of-rwandas-healthcare-system">3 days ago</a>
                    
                    
                        &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                    
                
                
                    
                        


<div class="mr-byline ">
    By <a href="/shriya-yarlagadda" target="_blank">Shriya Yarlagadda</a>
</div>


                    
                    
                
                
                    
                        &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                    
                
                



    
    
        <a href="/media-outlet/hir-harvard" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Harvard International Review</a>
        
    
    


            </div>
            
            
                
                    The Rwandan Genocide, born from intense strife and structural inequality between Hutus and Tutsis in Rwanda, is infamous for its brutality. Within 100 days, upwards of 800,000 people were violently murdered and the lives of hundreds of thousands more were permanently affected by physical and sexual violence.
                
                
            
        </div>
    
    
        <div class="news-story-meta col-xs-12">
            <span class="sharing-counts small " data-total-count="0">
  

